name: CUBE ONE JUMP
description:
CUBE ONE JUMP is an endless and score game.

Be sure to jump to time and speed and distance, which is the result of your reaction to the right jump.

This game is simple and attractive. Comes with great gameplay and extraordinary sound designed.

- Challenge your friends over Game Center!

*****
SUPPORTED DEVICES
iPad 2, iPad 3, iPad 4, iPad Air, iPad Mini (Retina)
iPhone 4S, iPhone 5, iPhone 5C, iPhone 5S, iPhone 6 & 6 Plus
iPod 5th Gen
